WEBVTT

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:31.496
I bought and ate

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:33.536
little sweets,

00:04:33.560 --> 00:04:38.200
seeking the familiar
comfort of their taste.

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:42.016
Central Africans ate these sweets

00:04:42.040 --> 00:04:43.240
to ease their hunger,

00:04:44.560 --> 00:04:49.240
leaving a trail of thousands
of plastic wrappers as they fled.

00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:54.656
On the few radio stations
still operating in the country,

00:04:54.680 --> 00:04:56.960
I mostly heard pop music.

00:04:58.680 --> 00:05:00.696
As the war mounted,